      ],
      "Replication": "Disabled",
      "Description": "允许直接编写 DesignScript 代码",
      "Code": "\"To keep Dynamo graphs neat and readable, we recommend following a clear\nstructure.\n\nFor more information, read the Dynamo Primer page on best-practice graph strategies:\nhttps://primer2.dynamobim.org/9_best_practices/1-graph-strategies\";"
    },
    {
